bio: Dedicated and Highly Motivated Web Developer with hands-on experience designing, building, and testing backend services for multiple apps. I strive to create scalable and well thought out products to help others.

After my previous position as a Software Administrator and working with Salesforce, I decided to expand my career path! I started at Turing school of Software and Design and learned many backend topics and technologies while meeting deadlines and collaborating with teams to build a successful product.
I've developed tools to help those in need and support groups that are dedicated to a craft. I'm excited to continue to do so further in my career and with a team who strives to help those in need
